data.description: Beautiful, Open townhome with one car attached garage.  Cul-de-sac and backed up to open wooded space with 16 miles of Cherry Creek Trails.  Beautiful wood floors and big, bright family room.  Big kitchen with stainless appliances.  Refrigerator will stay as well as the Washer and Dryer stacked in the pantry area.  No carpet except on the stairs.  Amazing back porch with TREK DECK backing up to open meadows with no neighbors directly behind you. This home has amazing location and owner will leave gazebo!
